	
WEBVTT

00:04:04.496 --> 00:04:07.567 align:middle line:84%
Spice for the front page, isn't it?

00:04:07.567 --> 00:04:10.717 align:middle line:90%
All you can think of are
headlines for the front page.

00:04:10.717 --> 00:04:12.150 align:middle line:84%
Oh, drop it!

00:04:12.150 --> 00:04:27.974 align:middle line:84%
Here comes Judge Raghunath.

00:04:27.974 --> 00:04:32.972 align:middle line:90%
Such a gentleman! Why on earth
did that goon want to kill him?

00:04:32.972 --> 00:05:07.624 align:middle line:84%
Here comes your friend.

00:05:07.624 --> 00:05:11.443 align:middle line:90%
Is the jury in place?
- Yes, my Lord. Present.

00:05:11.443 --> 00:05:13.530 align:middle line:90%
Is the accused present?
- Present, my Lord.

00:05:13.530 --> 00:05:20.790 align:middle line:84%
Who is the counsel for the accused?

00:05:20.790 --> 00:05:26.637 align:middle line:84%
Who is the counsel for the accused?

00:05:26.637 --> 00:05:33.143 align:middle line:90%
Have you no lawyer
to defend your case?

00:05:33.143 --> 00:05:46.862 align:middle line:90%
In that case, the government...
- My Lord.

00:05:46.862 --> 00:05:56.152 align:middle line:84%
I'm the counsel for the accused.

00:05:56.152 --> 00:05:59.137 align:middle line:84%
I do not wish to defend myself.

00:05:59.137 --> 00:06:06.941 align:middle line:90%
I promised to defend you,
if you're ever arraigned. Remember?

00:06:06.941 --> 00:06:15.201 align:middle line:84%
Does the accused give his consent?

00:06:15.201 --> 00:06:18.542 align:middle line:84%
Yes.

00:06:18.542 --> 00:06:25.631 align:middle line:90%
Raj, you have been accused of
a murderous attack on Judge Raghunath.

00:06:25.631 --> 00:06:34.988 align:middle line:84%
You may plead your case.

00:06:34.988 --> 00:06:41.748 align:middle line:84%
I swear to speak the truth.

00:06:41.748 --> 00:06:47.332 align:middle line:90%
Judge Raghunath, can you tell us
why the accused tried to kill you?

00:06:47.332 --> 00:06:49.634 align:middle line:84%
Did he have any enmity with you?

00:06:49.634 --> 00:06:56.523 align:middle line:90%
Yes. The grudge that a born
felon bears...

00:06:56.523 --> 00:07:02.107 align:middle line:90%
against the judge who sentences
him and grants no reprieve.

00:07:02.107 --> 00:07:05.177 align:middle line:90%
Could there be no other reason
for such animosity?

00:07:05.177 --> 00:07:12.328 align:middle line:84%
None. How else could I relate to him?

00:07:12.328 --> 00:07:16.117 align:middle line:84%
I have no further questions.

00:07:16.117 --> 00:07:30.677 align:middle line:90%
Defense may proceed with
cross-questioning.

00:07:30.677 --> 00:07:34.733 align:middle line:84%
Judge, you are senior to me.

00:07:34.733 --> 00:07:40.471 align:middle line:90%
If in the course of questioning,
I happen to affront you do forgive me.

00:07:40.471 --> 00:07:45.696 align:middle line:90%
Someone's life is at stake.
And you have taught me...

00:07:45.696 --> 00:07:53.575 align:middle line:90%
to ignore all relationships for
the dispensation of justice.

00:07:53.575 --> 00:08:03.252 align:middle line:90%
This is my first interrogation.
Please give me your blessings.

00:08:03.252 --> 00:08:08.413 align:middle line:90%
What do you mean when you call
the accused a born felon?

00:08:08.413 --> 00:08:10.929 align:middle line:84%
He has been a tramp and a hoodlum...

00:08:10.929 --> 00:08:13.781 align:middle line:90%
ever since he was a child.
His record says it.

00:08:13.781 --> 00:08:18.580 align:middle line:90%
This penchant for crime has surely
been transmitted congenitally.

00:08:18.580 --> 00:08:20.651 align:middle line:84%
Judge, do you have any children?

00:08:20.651 --> 00:08:22.515 align:middle line:84%
No

00:08:22.515 --> 00:08:25.369 align:middle line:90%
But how is this question relevant
to this case?

00:08:25.369 --> 00:08:32.420 align:middle line:90%
Most relevant. Think again. Are you
certain that you have no children?

00:08:32.420 --> 00:08:37.688 align:middle line:90%
No. But I reiterate. This question...
- Can you recount the circumstance...

00:08:37.688 --> 00:08:42.213 align:middle line:90%
when you threw your wife
out of your house?

00:08:42.213 --> 00:08:47.377 align:middle line:90%
My Lord, am I to be forced to reply
to such meaningless questions?

00:08:47.377 --> 00:08:52.225 align:middle line:90%
Ms Rita, you may ask questions
relevant only to the case.

00:08:52.225 --> 00:08:55.806 align:middle line:90%
We wish to know whether or not,
the accused attempted murder.

00:08:55.806 --> 00:08:57.350 align:middle line:84%
If yes, then why?

00:08:57.350 --> 00:09:03.163 align:middle line:90%
Enough! Stop it! I'm a murderer!
Hang me if you will!

00:09:03.163 --> 00:09:05.367 align:middle line:84%
Order! Order!

00:09:05.367 --> 00:09:07.395 align:middle line:84%
Proceed with your questioning.

00:09:07.395 --> 00:09:11.536 align:middle line:90%
The accused does not deny having
assaulted Judge Raghunath.

00:09:11.536 --> 00:09:17.815 align:middle line:90%
But, as you said just now,
the question is why he did it.

00:09:17.815 --> 00:09:20.472 align:middle line:90%
This interrogation is meant
to reveal the answer...

00:09:20.472 --> 00:09:25.844 align:middle line:90%
if you my Lord, and Judge Raghunath
repose your trust in me for a while

00:09:25.844 --> 00:09:29.680 align:middle line:84%
You may proceed.

00:09:29.680 --> 00:09:32.917 align:middle line:90%
I repeat my question.
Can you recount the circumstance...

00:09:32.917 --> 00:09:37.236 align:middle line:90%
when you threw your wife
out of your house?

00:09:37.236 --> 00:09:41.884 align:middle line:90%
I beg your pardon, Judge Raghunath,
but this question is very important.

00:09:41.884 --> 00:09:44.842 align:middle line:90%
And not only for the accused.
For you too.

00:09:44.842 --> 00:09:49.716 align:middle line:90%
The cause of whatever is happening
today, lies rooted in your past.

00:09:49.716 --> 00:09:52.733 align:middle line:84%
Remember?

00:09:52.733 --> 00:09:55.512 align:middle line:84%
Remember?

00:09:55.512 --> 00:10:00.125 align:middle line:90%
Can you tell us? Why, when
and under what circumstance...

00:10:00.125 --> 00:10:03.367 align:middle line:90%
did you throw your wife
out of your house?

00:10:03.367 --> 00:10:06.192 align:middle line:84%
Why, when and under what circumstance...

00:10:06.192 --> 00:10:09.422 align:middle line:90%
..did you throw your wife
out of your house?

00:10:09.422 --> 00:10:12.244 align:middle line:84%
Why, when and under what circumstance...

00:10:12.244 --> 00:10:16.980 align:middle line:90%
