wife out of your house?

00:10:16.980 --> 00:10:17.686 align:middle line:84%
24 years ago...

00:10:17.686 --> 00:10:19.729 align:middle line:84%
I was practicing law in Lucknow.

00:10:19.729 --> 00:10:24.928 align:middle line:90%
I was the black sheep of the family,
because I opposed social norm...

00:10:24.928 --> 00:10:29.349 align:middle line:90%
and I had married a widow.
My father was a big gun.

00:10:29.349 --> 00:10:32.793 align:middle line:90%
And was away in Bombay most of the time.
He was unhappy with me.

00:10:32.793 --> 00:10:36.107 align:middle line:90%
But under no circumstance,
was I willing to leave Leela.

00:10:36.107 --> 00:10:40.402 align:middle line:90%
She was so good to me.
She was such a good woman.

00:10:40.402 --> 00:10:44.675 align:middle line:84%
And I was in love with her.

00:10:44.675 --> 00:10:48.215 align:middle line:90%
But once, on our way from
Kanpur to Allahabad...

00:10:48.215 --> 00:10:50.709 align:middle line:90%
