00:14:03.688 --> 00:14:08.883 align:middle line:90%
What are you thinking about?
- Why do they sing "Beware"?

00:14:08.883 --> 00:14:15.329 align:middle line:90%
They say, these parts are dangerous.
Jagga the bandit. He's from these parts.

00:14:15.329 --> 00:14:19.608 align:middle line:90%
Bandits?
- Yes, but don't worry.

00:14:19.608 --> 00:14:22.184 align:middle line:90%
