00:14:30.234 --> 00:14:38.322 align:middle line:90%
In case you're afraid, I can come over.
- No.

00:14:38.322 --> 00:14:46.582 align:middle line:84%
Leela!

00:14:46.582 --> 00:15:22.810 align:middle line:84%
No! The lady is with them!

00:15:22.810 --> 00:15:35.204 align:middle line:84%
Leave me! Leave me! Leave me!

00:15:35.204 --> 00:15:39.402 align:middle line:84%
You heartless bandits!

00:15:39.402 --> 00:15:43.882 align:middle line:84%
Where's your chief?

00:15:43.882 --> 00:15:47.388 align:middle line:90%
What right have you to terrorise
women from good families?

00:15:47.388 --> 00:15:49.734 align:middle line:90%
Aren't you ashamed?
- Ashamed?

00:15:49.734 --> 00:15:53.611 align:middle line:90%
Shame is for good folks,
not for bandits and robbers.

00:15:53.611 --> 00:15:59.458 align:middle line:90%
As for me, my grandfather was a bandit,
my father was a bandit! But I wasn't.

00:15:59.458 --> 00:16:04.575 align:middle line:90%
And your husband went and made me one!
- My husband?

00:16:04.575 --> 00:16:08.713 align:middle line:90%
Who are you?
- Jagga. And I was innocent.

00:16:08.713 --> 00:16:14.214 align:middle line:90%
But without a shard of evidence,
your husband framed me...

00:16:14.214 --> 00:16:18.915 align:middle line:90%
just because my father, my grandfather
were bandits.

00:16:18.915 --> 00:16:22.740 align:middle line:90%
He framed me for rape
and he sent me to jail.

00:16:22.740 --> 00:16:30.675 align:middle line:90%
So I've decided to prove
your husband right.

00:16:30.675 --> 00:16:38.492 align:middle line:84%
Coward!

00:16:38.492 --> 00:16:42.559 align:middle line:84%
See what's wrong with her.

00:16:42.559 --> 00:16:45.788 align:middle line:84%
Has she come to her senses?

00:16:45.788 --> 00:16:50.503 align:middle line:84%
No, she's still in a swoon.

00:16:50.503 --> 00:16:56.134 align:middle line:90%
Let her go, Chief. She's pregnant.
She's going to become a mother.

00:16:56.134 --> 00:17:00.946 align:middle line:84%
Touch her, and you go to hell.

00:17:00.946 --> 00:17:06.881 align:middle line:84%
Pregnant? With a baby?

00:17:06.881 --> 00:17:14.598 align:middle line:90%
Her husband said that children born
of good folks turn out good.

00:17:14.598 --> 00:17:18.916 align:middle line:84%
And children born of bandits...

00:17:18.916 --> 00:17:22.442 align:middle line:84%
turn out to be bandits. Always.

00:17:22.442 --> 00:17:30.376 align:middle line:90%
Now let's see what the lawyer's son
turns out to be.

00:17:30.376 --> 00:17:35.545 align:middle line:84%
Send her back once she recovers.

00:17:35.545 --> 00:17:49.179 align:middle line:90%
Good are those born of good folks!
And of bandits are bandits born.

00:17:49.179 --> 00:17:52.202 align:middle line:90%
You should make me a gift.
- What's the occasion?

00:17:52.202 --> 00:17:55.689 align:middle line:90%
Not any occasion.
The lady is back.

00:17:55.689 --> 00:17:59.367 align:middle line:84%
What did you say? The lady?

00:17:59.367 --> 00:18:02.379 align:middle line:84%
Leela!

00:18:02.379 --> 00:18:07.214 align:middle line:84%
Leela!

00:18:07.214 --> 00:18:09.134 align:middle line:84%
Why is it dark in here?

00:18:09.134 --> 00:18:10.924 align:middle line:84%
Nathu! Bansi! Naina!

00:18:10.924 --> 00:18:16.679 align:middle line:84%
Lights! Tonight we celebrate!

00:18:16.679 --> 00:18:18.466 align:middle line:84%
Leela.

00:18:18.466 --> 00:18:23.793 align:middle line:84%
It is you who lights up my life.

00:18:23.793 --> 00:18:32.544 align:middle line:84%
Leela.

00:18:32.544 --> 00:18:36.452 align:middle line:90%
Now that you're back,
even the lights seem so bright!

00:18:36.452 --> 00:18:45.682 align:middle line:84%
Give me the wick.

00:18:45.682 --> 00:18:53.297 align:middle line:90%
But Leela, how did you escape?
I hope you weren't in danger?

00:18:53.297 --> 00:18:59.882 align:middle line:90%
Your love was with me.
How could anyone even look up at me?

00:18:59.882 --> 00:19:11.376 align:middle line:90%
You are tired. Change.
I'll bring you your dressing gown.

00:19:11.376 --> 00:19:17.773 align:middle line:84%
These last four days.

00:19:17.773 --> 00:19:22.645 align:middle line:90%
The last four days were
like a lifetime.

00:19:22.645 --> 00:19:25.483 align:middle line:90%
I took the police and I looked
everywhere for you.

00:19:25.483 --> 00:19:38.206 align:middle line:84%
All the while, I feared...

00:19:38.206 --> 00:19:49.904 align:middle line:84%
I feared you were in grave danger!

00:19:49.904 --> 00:19:55.746 align:middle line:90%
But how did you escape?
And who was this bandit?

00:19:55.746 --> 00:20:00.768 align:middle line:90%
Some Jagga.
He said that you had convicted him.

00:20:00.768 --> 00:20:03.106 align:middle line:84%
Jagga.

00:20:03.106 --> 00:20:09.549 align:middle line:90%
So he escaped to get even with me!
If he has done anything to you...

00:20:09.549 --> 00:20:14.340 align:middle line:90%
I'll see to it that he hangs!
- At heart, he's a devil.

00:20:14.340 --> 00:20:19.437 align:middle line:90%
But God saved me at the last moment.
Thank God!

00:20:19.437 --> 00:20:23.439 align:middle line:84%
Tell me something.

00:20:23.439 --> 00:20:25.283 align:middle line:84%
Ask.

00:20:25.283 --> 00:20:30.945 align:middle line:90%
Does a bandit's son necessarily
become a bandit?

00:20:30.945 --> 00:20:36.689 align:middle line:84%
Yes, it's bound to happen.

00:20:36.689 --> 00:20:51.263 align:middle line:90%
But why do you ask?
- Just like that.

00:20:51.263 --> 00:20:56.295 align:middle line:90%
Let's see what comes first.
Your becoming a magistrate, or...

00:20:56.295 --> 00:21:00.760 align:middle line:84%
Why? Is someone expected?

00:21:00.760 --> 00:21:03.246 align:middle line:84%
A new guest.

00:21:03.246 --> 00:21:08.288 align:middle line:90%
Now I don't have any chances
of becoming a magistrate.

00:21:08.288 --> 00:21:11.733 align:middle line:84%
Why? What happened?

00:21:11.733 --> 00:21:22.225 align:middle line:90%
Whatever...
let's talk of something else.

00:21:22.225 --> 00:21:25.998 align:middle line:84%
How do you like this?

00:21:25.998 --> 00:21:27.908 align:middle line:84%
Nice.

00:21:27.908 --> 00:21:30.221 align:middle line:84%
Nice.

00:21:30.221 --> 00:21:37.194 align:middle line:90%
Listen...
Are you annoyed with me?

00:21:37.194 --> 00:21:41.245 align:middle line:84%
Annoyed? No.

00:21:41.245 --> 00:21:47.258 align:middle line:84%
Why should I be annoyed with you?

00:21:47.258 --> 00:21:58.592 align:middle line:84%
Have my lunch sent over.

00:21:58.592 --> 00:22:00.512 align:middle line:90%
What's the matter?
Where are the servants?

00:22:00.512 --> 00:22:04.643 align:middle line:90%
God knows! Maybe they're all dead!
I have to do all the chores.

00:22:04.643 --> 00:22:07.159 align:middle line:90%
Let me help you.
- You'd rather tell her all this.

00:22:07.159 --> 00:22:10.955 align:middle line:84%
She's sitting around like a queen!

00:22:10.955 --> 00:22:15.511 align:middle line:90%
Not to be cross with Leela.
I told her not to strain herself.

00:22:15.511 --> 00:22:19.959 align:middle line:90%
You know the condition she is in.
And in a few days from now...

00:22:19.959 --> 00:22:25.540 align:middle line:90%
She's going to bear the fruit
of her sins!

00:22:25.540 --> 00:22:29.293 align:middle line:90%
What are you saying?!
- What everyone else is saying!

00:22:29.293 --> 00:22:34.369 align:middle line:90%
For four days, she lived with a bandit!
And Jagga that!

00:22:34.369 --> 00:22:38.590 align:middle line:90%
Don't you remember what
he was convicted for?

00:22:38.590 --> 00:22:41.703 align:middle line:90%
Do you enjoy making someone unhappy?
The jaundiced eye sees all yellow.

00:22:41.703 --> 00:22:45.559 align:middle line:90%
Do you think you're beyond scrutiny?
Don't you forget...

00:22:45.559 --> 00:22:47.628 align:middle line:90%
women have had to stand the test of
chastity. Because society asks for it.

00:22:47.628 --> 00:22:53.909 align:middle line:84%
Bhabhi! (Sister-in-law)

00:22:53.909 --> 00:22:56.889 align:middle line:90%
Forgive me Bhabhi,
your pot is broken.

00:22:56.889 --> 00:23:01.616 align:middle line:90%
It's only an earthen pot. But remember,
a woman's honour is far more fragile.

00:23:01.616 --> 00:23:32.730 align:middle line:90%
Once disgraced, her honour
can never be redeemed.

00:23:32.730 --> 00:23:36.343 align:middle line:84%
Just answer my question!

00:23:36.343 --> 00:23:39.835 align:middle line:90%
Did you not know that your wife
was seeing her lover on the sly?

00:23:39.835 --> 00:23:44.314 align:middle line:90%
The villagers used to say that.
But I didn't heed what they said.

00:23:44.314 --> 00:23:47.969 align:middle line:90%
You haven't yet told the court
why your wife deserted you.

00:23:47.969 --> 00:24:02.450 align:middle line:90%
You know it! Women are adulterous!
