01:02:44.407 --> 01:02:54.979 align:middle line:84%
There you are! Hiding!

01:02:54.979 --> 01:02:57.329 align:middle line:90%
Aren't you ashamed? Give it to me.
Else, I'll beat you to pulp.

01:02:57.329 --> 01:03:00.149 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to kill you! Give me!

01:03:00.149 --> 01:03:08.866 align:middle line:84%
Where are you running away?

01:03:08.866 --> 01:03:13.999 align:middle line:84%
Give the purse!

01:03:13.999 --> 01:03:18.536 align:middle line:84%
You dare stare at me like that?

01:03:18.536 --> 01:03:33.872 align:middle line:84%
Hey... knife!

01:03:33.872 --> 01:03:37.245 align:middle line:84%
Are you running away? Coward!

01:03:37.245 --> 01:03:39.487 align:middle line:84%
Coward!

01:03:39.487 --> 01:03:46.594 align:middle line:84%
Scoundrel!

01:03:46.594 --> 01:03:49.777 align:middle line:84%
He ran away

01:03:49.777 --> 01:03:52.624 align:middle line:84%
Anyway, here's your purse"

01:03:52.624 --> 01:03:54.686 align:middle line:84%
Keep it.

01:03:54.686 --> 01:04:00.634 align:middle line:90%
You've been through so much
trouble for my sake.

01:04:00.634 --> 01:04:05.717 align:middle line:84%
No trouble. I've taken more.

01:04:05.717 --> 01:04:12.197 align:middle line:90%
I should apologise. You risked
your life to get my purse back.

01:04:12.197 --> 01:04:17.448 align:middle line:90%
And I suspected you.
- Not your fault.

01:04:17.448 --> 01:04:19.352 align:middle line:84%
It's just my looks.

01:04:19.352 --> 01:04:22.448 align:middle line:90%
Sometimes even the police
are mistaken.

01:04:22.448 --> 01:04:26.280 align:middle line:84%
Bye

01:04:26.280 --> 01:04:29.845 align:middle line:90%
How was the show?
- No use.

01:04:29.845 --> 01:04:33.338 align:middle line:90%
We'll find a car. Why worry?
Get over to the place.

01:04:33.338 --> 01:04:37.286 align:middle line:90%
I'll join you after a change
of clothes.

01:04:37.286 --> 01:04:40.442 align:middle line:90%
Hey Romeo! You tear your clothes
no sooner than you see a girl!

01:04:40.442 --> 01:05:04.663 align:middle line:90%
Get lost.
- Get going.

01:05:04.663 --> 01:06:01.699 align:middle line:84%
Stop! Thief!

01:06:01.699 --> 01:06:05.602 align:middle line:84%
Where are you going?

01:06:05.602 --> 01:06:07.982 align:middle line:84%
Inside.

01:06:07.982 --> 01:06:12.692 align:middle line:90%
Inside? What do you want?
- Strange question.

01:06:12.692 --> 01:06:15.283 align:middle line:90%
Your boss is the one who called me.
And you ask me what I want?

01:06:15.283 --> 01:06:18.149 align:middle line:84%
The boss, or the lady? Who called you?

01:06:18.149 --> 01:06:19.719 align:middle line:84%
Yes, the lady.

01:06:19.719 --> 01:06:23.173 align:middle line:90%
So you're the one
who fixes the piano?

01:06:23.173 --> 01:06:27.309 align:middle line:84%
Yes! The piano fixer!

01:06:27.309 --> 01:06:28.802 align:middle line:90%
Is the piano in there?
- Are pianos kept outside?

01:06:28.802 --> 01:06:56.148 align:middle line:90%
No! Inside. Come on in,
else I'll get into trouble.

01:06:56.148 --> 01:07:06.981 align:middle line:84%
Looks like a billionaire's palace!

01:07:06.981 --> 01:07:17.398 align:middle line:90%
Hello, darling.
- What did you say?

01:07:17.398 --> 01:07:20.646 align:middle line:84%
The mantle!

01:07:20.646 --> 01:07:24.486 align:middle line:84%
What a lovely mantle!

01:07:24.486 --> 01:07:30.912 align:middle line:84%
What a grand mansion!

01:07:30.912 --> 01:07:33.725 align:middle line:84%
The mantle!

01:07:33.725 --> 01:07:39.909 align:middle line:90%
What kind of a joke is this?
Here's the piano.

01:07:39.909 --> 01:07:43.556 align:middle line:90%
This piano is in bad shape.
Badly damaged.

01:07:43.556 --> 01:07:45.417 align:middle line:84%
Look.

01:07:45.417 --> 01:07:50.986 align:middle line:90%
Rotten! It'll take me time to fix it.
Go on, get back to work.

01:07:50.986 --> 01:08:15.839 align:middle line:84%
I'll fix it.

01:08:15.839 --> 01:08:21.692 align:middle line:84%
Who's playing my piano?

01:08:21.692 --> 01:08:33.549 align:middle line:90%
You?
- You!

01:08:33.549 --> 01:08:39.200 align:middle line:90%
I'm mistaken, once again
I thought it must be a thief.

01:08:39.200 --> 01:08:40.908 align:middle line:90%
That's what I am.
- What?

01:08:40.908 --> 01:08:44.637 align:middle line:90%
I mean, who else but a thief
would come in uninvited?

01:08:44.637 --> 01:08:47.860 align:middle line:84%
No, it's good of you to have come.

01:08:47.860 --> 01:08:52.343 align:middle line:90%
You did me a favour.
I should've called you over.

01:08:52.343 --> 01:08:57.575 align:middle line:90%
But I didn't know your address.
How did you find out my address?

01:08:57.575 --> 01:09:02.725 align:middle line:90%
What?
- How did you find out my address?

01:09:02.725 --> 01:09:05.986 align:middle line:90%
No, don't ask me that.
It's a secret.

01:09:05.986 --> 01:09:08.948 align:middle line:90%
Let's say, it's luck that has led me
to your doorstep.

01:09:08.948 --> 01:09:25.514 align:middle line:90%
Please be seated
- Thanks.

01:09:25.514 --> 01:09:28.543 align:middle line:84%
Cigarette?

01:09:28.543 --> 01:09:30.790 align:middle line:84%
Lighter?

01:09:30.790 --> 01:09:34.447 align:middle line:84%
No, thanks. Matches.

01:09:34.447 --> 01:09:37.349 align:middle line:90%
Madam, he's the piano-fixer...
- Piano fixer?

01:09:37.349 --> 01:09:39.912 align:middle line:90%
Your servant thinks I'm here
to fix the piano.

01:09:39.912 --> 01:09:47.666 align:middle line:90%
But you said...
- Never mind, take the call. Go on.

01:09:47.666 --> 01:09:51.946 align:middle line:90%
Strange fellow.
He took you for a piano mechanic.

01:09:51.946 --> 01:09:56.689 align:middle line:90%
Not his fault.
It's just my looks.

01:09:56.689 --> 01:09:58.873 align:middle line:84%
Inspector sahib, no thief came in here.

01:09:58.873 --> 01:10:00.679 align:middle line:84%
Please wait here.

01:10:00.679 --> 01:10:03.334 align:middle line:84%
Inspector?

01:10:03.334 --> 01:10:08.542 align:middle line:90%
What brings the police here?
Excuse me, I'll be back.

01:10:08.542 --> 01:10:15.338 align:middle line:90%
A car thief has sneaked into one
of the houses in this neighbourhood.

01:10:15.338 --> 01:10:20.796 align:middle line:90%
Have you seen anyone?
- No, no one came in here.

01:10:20.796 --> 01:10:25.713 align:middle line:90%
She's wrong about
no one coming in here.

01:10:25.713 --> 01:10:28.945 align:middle line:90%
I happen to be a visitor.
Would you be looking for me?

01:10:28.945 --> 01:10:31.513 align:middle line:84%
No... how could this be?

01:10:31.513 --> 01:10:36.417 align:middle line:84%
Okay. Forgive me.

01:10:36.417 --> 01:10:39.833 align:middle line:84%
Come.

01:10:39.833 --> 01:10:43.391 align:middle line:90%
Grand house.
- Yes. It belongs to the Judge.

01:10:43.391 --> 01:10:46.723 align:middle line:90%
Judge?
- Yes, he's my guardian.

01:10:46.723 --> 01:10:48.487 align:middle line:84%
Guardian?

01:10:48.487 --> 01:10:52.381 align:middle line:90%
Like the guard on the train
...signalling red and green?

01:10:52.381 --> 01:10:56.271 align:middle line:90%
No. After my father passed away,
I have been his ward.

01:10:56.271 --> 01:10:59.304 align:middle line:90%
For the sake of my education,
he left Lucknow and he came to Bombay.

01:10:59.304 --> 01:11:02.871 align:middle line:84%
I am much obliged to him.

01:11:02.871 --> 01:11:07.623 align:middle line:90%
Do judges sport such grand houses?
He must be making a pile on the side.

01:11:07.623 --> 01:11:10.928 align:middle line:90%
What a thing to say!
The judge is very principled.

01:11:10.928 --> 01:11:17.687 align:middle line:90%
He never spares criminals.
- I hope God spares him!

01:11:17.687 --> 01:11:23.902 align:middle line:90%
Not to worry. If you're ever arraigned
in his court, let me defend your case.

01:11:23.902 --> 01:11:30.162 align:middle line:90%
You... lawyer?
- Yes.

01:11:30.162 --> 01:11:34.521 align:middle line:84%
I took you for a schoolgirl.

01:11:34.521 --> 01:11:37.736 align:middle line:90%
That was a nice one. A couple
of months, and I'll be an advocate.

01:11:37.736 --> 01:11:41.320 align:middle line:84%
Would you like to see my degree?

01:11:41.320 --> 01:11:47.351 align:middle line:90%
A judge lives here. And a lawyer too.
Leaves only one to make a full court!

01:11:47.351 --> 01:11:50.529 align:middle line:90%
Yours truly. And here I am.
- And what are you up to?

01:11:50.529 --> 01:11:52.978 align:middle line:84%
I steal.

01:11:52.978 --> 01:11:55.555 align:middle line:90%
Stealing, picking pockets, locks,
ladies' purses, like yours...

01:11:55.555 --> 01:11:58.787 align:middle line:90%
that's what I'm up to.
- You're joking again. Be seated.

01:11:58.787 --> 01:12:03.561 align:middle line:90%
You don't think I'm a thief?
- No, I think you're a gentleman.

01:12:03.561 --> 01:12:07.303 align:middle line:84%
This is the new world order!

01:12:07.303 --> 01:12:10.961 align:middle line:90%
The thieves, the hoodwinkers, they
all dress in first class suits like...

01:12:10.961 --> 01:12:14.392 align:middle line:90%
...I'm wearing and
we take them for gentlemen.

01:12:14.392 --> 01:12:19.426 align:middle line:90%
But those who work hard for an
honest living and dress shabbily...

01:12:19.426 --> 01:12:25.226 align:middle line:90%
...are labelled tramps and wastrels.
The capitalists, the blackmarketeers...

01:12:25.226 --> 01:12:30.855 align:middle line:90%
the profiteers, the usurers...
who are they? Thieves, like I am!

01:12:30.855 --> 01:12:36.132 align:middle line:90%
You sound like a stock broker
or a banker.

01:12:36.132 --> 01:12:37.759 align:middle line:90%
You might say that give and take
of money is what I'm concerned with.

01:12:37.759 --> 01:12:41.235 align:middle line:90%
As far as banks are concerned,
I visit banks regularly.

01:12:41.235 --> 01:12:44.801 align:middle line:84%
Be seated.

01:12:44.801 --> 01:13:02.487 align:middle line:84%
Tell me your name.

01:13:02.487 --> 01:13:13.141 align:middle line:90%
Tell me, whose photo is this?
- Mine.

01:13:13.141 --> 01:13:17.498 align:middle line:90%
You?
- Yes, when I was young.

01:13:17.498 --> 01:13:20.675 align:middle line:84%
It's a birthday photo.

01:13:20.675 --> 01:13:31.733 align:middle line:90%
Your name?
- Rita. Why?

01:13:31.733 --> 01:13:37.109 align:middle line:90%
Ms Rita, would you like to come
to my house?

01:13:37.109 --> 01:13:41.151 align:middle line:90%
I'd like to show you
something unique.

01:13:41.151 --> 01:13:56.126 align:middle line:90%
My mother would be very pleased
to meet you. Come

01:13:56.126 --> 01:13:58.810 align:middle line:84%
Raj!

01:13:58.810 --> 01:14:00.593 align:middle line:84%
Rita!

01:14:00.593 --> 01:14:11.837 align:middle line:90%
You?
- After twelve years.

01:14:11.837 --> 01:14:15.169 align:middle line:84%
You've changed!

01:14:15.169 --> 01:14:21.293 align:middle line:84%
You haven't changed at all.

01:14:21.293 --> 01:14:25.120 align:middle line:84%
Where have you been, Raj?

01:14:25.120 --> 01:14:28.489 align:middle line:84%
Looking for you.

01:14:28.489 --> 01:14:32.161 align:middle line:90%
And at last, I've found you
- And when I saw you...

01:14:32.161 --> 01:14:35.120 align:middle line:84%
I took you for a thief.

01:14:35.120 --> 01:14:40.859 align:middle line:90%
Not your fault.
It's in my looks.

01:14:40.859 --> 01:15:28.893 align:middle line:84%
Raj!

01:15:28.893 --> 01:15:35.670 align:middle line:90%
"Since my beloved came home,
my heart flutters."

01:15:35.670 --> 01:15:53.245 align:middle line:90%
"Since my beloved came home,
my heart flutters."

01:15:53.245 --> 01:15:57.676 align:middle line:84%
"The heart had spoken to a heart."

01:15:57.676 --> 01:16:02.347 align:middle line:84%
"The heart had spoken to a heart."

01:16:02.347 --> 01:16:06.716 align:middle line:84%
"The old times have come back."

01:16:06.716 --> 01:16:10.853 align:middle line:84%
"The old times have come back."

01:16:10.853 --> 01:16:17.395 align:middle line:90%
"He brought the happiness with
him, my heart flutters."

01:16:17.395 --> 01:16:34.403 align:middle line:90%
"Since my beloved came home,
my heart flutters."

01:16:34.403 --> 01:16:38.840 align:middle line:90%
"From the eyes, he dwelled
in my heart."

01:16:38.840 --> 01:16:43.158 align:middle line:90%
"From the eyes, he dwelled
in my heart."

01:16:43.158 --> 01:16:47.151 align:middle line:84%
"I smile and scatter the stars."

01:16:47.151 --> 01:16:51.822 align:middle line:84%
"I smile and scatter the stars."

01:16:51.822 --> 01:16:58.762 align:middle line:90%
"Feelings dance and sing,
my heart flutters."

01:16:58.762 --> 01:17:16.601 align:middle line:90%
"Since my beloved came home,
my heart flutters."

01:17:16.601 --> 01:17:19.947 align:middle line:90%
"The days belong to us
and love is young."

01:17:19.947 --> 01:17:24.441 align:middle line:90%
"The days belong to us
and love is young."

01:17:24.441 --> 01:17:28.387 align:middle line:90%
"My world is flourishing
due to him."

01:17:28.387 --> 01:17:33.562 align:middle line:90%
"My world is flourishing
due to him."

01:17:33.562 --> 01:17:39.387 align:middle line:90%
"The thief returned to my heart,
my heart flutters."

01:17:39.387 --> 01:17:46.320 align:middle line:90%
"Since my beloved came home,
my heart flutters."

01:17:46.320 --> 01:17:53.560 align:middle line:90%
"Since my beloved came home,
my heart flutters."

01:17:53.560 --> 01:17:58.779 align:middle line:84%
The Judge is here.

01:17:58.779 --> 01:18:00.764 align:middle line:84%
So here you are. And you're late.

01:18:00.764 --> 01:18:06.663 align:middle line:90%
The doctor has told you to come home
and rest for at least an hour.

01:18:06.663 --> 01:18:09.618 align:middle line:90%
But you won't listen.
You look so tired.

01:18:09.618 --> 01:18:11.504 align:middle line:90%
Hello, Rita.
- Hello, Rita!

01:18:11.504 --> 01:18:16.708 align:middle line:90%
Just sit here. I'll get you
your dressing gown.

01:18:16.708 --> 01:18:19.444 align:middle line:90%
Tell me, where have you been
all this time?

01:18:19.444 --> 01:18:24.737 align:middle line:90%
I had a lecture in the law college.
I went there directly from the court.

01:18:24.737 --> 01:18:29.324 align:middle line:90%
All that jabbering
is giving me a headache.

01:18:29.324 --> 01:18:34.643 align:middle line:90%
That's bound to happen. The doctor
told you to eat before eight.

01:18:34.643 --> 01:18:39.548 align:middle line:84%
It's nine thirty now.

01:18:39.548 --> 01:18:45.443 align:middle line:90%
Listen to that!
Even the clock is angry with you.

01:18:45.443 --> 01:19:06.666 align:middle line:84%
Come on.

01:19:06.666 --> 01:19:11.819 align:middle line:90%
Tell me about yourself. What have
you been up to all evening?

01:19:11.819 --> 01:19:18.742 align:middle line:90%
You look as if you've found
a treasure.

01:19:18.742 --> 01:19:23.234 align:middle line:90%
You could say that. A long-lost friend
is no less than a treasure.

01:19:23.234 --> 01:19:34.693 align:middle line:90%
You'll be glad when you meet Raj.
You're certain to like him!

01:19:34.693 --> 01:19:42.876 align:middle line:90%
Who is this Mr. Raj? Where does he live?
What does he do? What's his family name?

01:19:42.876 --> 01:19:47.172 align:middle line:90%
He's a childhood friend.
We were in school together.

01:19:47.172 --> 01:19:50.107 align:middle line:84%
I'm seeing him after twelve years!

01:19:50.107 --> 01:19:53.951 align:middle line:84%
After twelve years?

01:19:53.951 --> 01:19:56.702 align:middle line:90%
After so many years,
most people change.

01:19:56.702 --> 01:20:00.635 align:middle line:90%
Raj has changed too. At school,
he used to be very quiet.

01:20:00.635 --> 01:20:04.565 align:middle line:90%
Now he has great sense of humour.
When I asked him what he's up to...

01:20:04.565 --> 01:20:07.290 align:middle line:84%
he said he's a thief.

01:20:07.290 --> 01:20:12.366 align:middle line:90%
Maybe that wasn't a joke?
- I don't follow you.

01:20:12.366 --> 01:20:15.223 align:middle line:84%
Never mind.

01:20:15.223 --> 01:20:18.427 align:middle line:90%
You know what young men
are like, these days.

01:20:18.427 --> 01:21:59.464 align:middle line:90%
Who knows, they might steal
something valuable.

01:21:59.464 --> 01:22:03.671 align:middle line:90%
The water is deep.
You might drown.

01:22:03.671 --> 01:22:10.903 align:middle line:90%
Not without you
- Is that so? Try that.

01:22:10.903 --> 01:22:31.578 align:middle line:84%
Is that so?

01:22:31.578 --> 01:22:33.991 align:middle line:90%
Hey lady, haven't you finished
dressing yet?

01:22:33.991 --> 01:22:38.355 align:middle line:90%
Where are you headed?
Gentlemen don't barge in...

01:22:38.355 --> 01:22:42.821 align:middle line:90%
when ladies are changing dresses.
Don't you know that?

01:22:42.821 --> 01:22:53.100 align:middle line:84%
How would I know?

01:22:53.100 --> 01:23:01.726 align:middle line:90%
I'm no gentleman.
- Savage.

01:23:01.726 --> 01:23:05.369 align:middle line:84%
Savage.

01:23:05.369 --> 01:23:12.163 align:middle line:90%
I'm not about to give in
to your type.

01:23:12.163 --> 01:23:15.668 align:middle line:84%
Where are you running away?

01:23:15.668 --> 01:23:20.435 align:middle line:90%
Let go of my hand. What kind
of a stupid joke is this?

01:23:20.435 --> 01:23:21.355 align:middle line:84%
You savage!

01:23:21.355 --> 01:23:24.178 align:middle line:90%
Am I?
- Yes! You're a savage!

01:23:24.178 --> 01:23:27.663 align:middle line:90%
Savage?
I'm a penniless, uneducated tramp!

01:23:27.663 --> 01:23:30.196 align:middle line:84%
I don't fit into high society!

01:23:30.196 --> 01:23:32.675 align:middle line:90%
How dare I maul your fragile body
with my beastly hands.

01:23:32.675 --> 01:23:35.216 align:middle line:90%
I told Ma that childhood friends,
like childhood days are gone...

01:23:35.216 --> 01:23:38.475 align:middle line:84%
never to return.

01:23:38.475 --> 01:23:43.246 align:middle line:84%
Good of you to have told me my class.

01:23:43.246 --> 01:23:46.768 align:middle line:84%
It was a joke. Don't get angry.

01:23:46.768 --> 01:23:58.336 align:middle line:84%
You want to hit me? Go ahead.

01:23:58.336 --> 01:24:02.417 align:middle line:84%
Whom will I hit?

01:24:02.417 --> 01:24:04.598 align:middle line:84%
You?

01:24:04.598 --> 01:24:37.583 align:middle line:84%
Or myself?

01:24:37.583 --> 01:24:42.643 align:middle line:84%
Hey! Hey!

01:24:42.643 --> 01:24:45.731 align:middle line:84%
Are you happy?

01:24:45.731 --> 01:24:48.875 align:middle line:84%
No.

01:24:48.875 --> 01:24:53.765 align:middle line:90%
Where are you lost?
- Up there

01:24:53.765 --> 01:24:58.776 align:middle line:90%
Come back.
- Where to?

01:24:58.776 --> 01:25:02.663 align:middle line:90%
Beside me.
- Why?

01:25:02.663 --> 01:25:13.772 align:middle line:84%
No reason.

01:25:13.772 --> 01:25:19.852 align:middle line:84%
Aren't you ashamed?

01:25:19.852 --> 01:25:25.697 align:middle line:90%
What are you looking at?
The Moon?

01:25:25.697 --> 01:25:30.226 align:middle line:84%
No. Clouds.

01:25:30.226 --> 01:25:33.102 align:middle line:90%
What's your problem?
You don't see the Moon...

01:25:33.102 --> 01:25:38.988 align:middle line:90%
and you see the dark clouds?
Won't you tell me?

01:25:38.988 --> 01:25:42.905 align:middle line:84%
Who else can I tell?

01:25:42.905 --> 01:25:45.896 align:middle line:90%
Rita.
- Yes.

01:25:45.896 --> 01:25:48.795 align:middle line:90%
We're seeing each other
after twelve years.

01:25:48.795 --> 01:25:50.775 align:middle line:84%
So what?

